{"word":"ὄπισθεν","slug":"ὄπισθεν","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ὄπισϑεν</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ fr.\">fr.</a> *<el>ὀπ-</el> (as in <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ὀψέ\">ὀψέ</a>, ὄπωρα</el>), which conveys a sense of being near or toward, plus -<el>ϑε</el>(<el>ν</el>) denoting source] <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adv.\">adv.</a> <b>from behind <a href='B:470 9:20'>Mt 9:20</a>; <a href='B:480 5:27'>Mk 5:27</a>; <a href='B:490 8:44'>Lk 8:44</a>; behind <a href='B:730 4:6'>Rv 4:6</a>;</b> of writing on a scroll, <b>on the back <a href='B:730 5:1'>5:1</a>;</b> as <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ prep.\">prep.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ gen.\">gen.</a> <b>behind <a href='B:470 15:23'>Mt 15:23</a>; <a href='B:490 23:26'>Lk 23:26</a>; <a href='B:730 1:10'>Rv 1:10</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a></b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ὀπή\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ὀπίσω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}